{"tid":1209603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日唔好去港交所","createTime":"2019-06-12T11:53:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T11:57:53.000Z","uid":182007,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a89bdaddfc99ddc992606e2af12a8b3253cc5509","tid":1209603,"uid":182007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T11:53:15.000Z","msg":"恆指會大跌 中國企業會仆街 國際大戶會估空 ！！"},{"pid":"a29ac47818416dd3d79a01866437c721a4308b73","tid":1209603,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T11:53:44.000Z","msg":"石禮謙話畀大家知，香港人最緊張嘅係經濟<br />\n<br />\n講個知識畀大家知<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">每塞6分鐘車，就會有28億損失</span></span><br />\n<br />\n舊Source： <a href=\"https://www.master-insight.com/塞車造成多少經濟損失？/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.master-insight.com%2F%E5%A1%9E%E8%BB%8A%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B1%EF%BC%9F%2F&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIr3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=411491e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.master-insight.com/塞車造成多少經濟損失？/</a><br />\n<br />\n重鐵同時間載到40幾萬人，繁忙時間以每平方米4個人計嘅運載量到9成<br />\n<br />\n只要帶手提行李就會每平方米大約企到2個人，即係20幾萬人會打爆重鐵<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">舉個例子</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">100萬人遊行散場，要現有運載力嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">5倍</span>先可以運走啲人</span></span>，但留意返香港有7百幾萬人，又有遊客。一百萬人散場，實際所需運載力係要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大過5倍</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家請守法體驗一流港鐵服務<br />\n[香港命脈][野餐以外]一星期暢遊港鐵體驗包 [鐵膠推介]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1205357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1205357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a75dff5179509d9e2b385fb05c0aaeee1e65f11e","tid":1209603,"uid":45105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T11:57:00.000Z","msg":"打算帶喼 <br />\n喼入面全部都係書<br />\n但又擔心佢好重<br />\n搭地鐵果陣搬唔到上車<br />\n搞到對門閂幾次都閂唔到"},{"pid":"2daee4d97cc6f9a2098fe3a9bc0138ed9cc2467a","tid":1209603,"uid":182006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T11:57:53.000Z","msg":"Pish"}]}